2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | sports | zombie | epic |

